<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA28">
<l>aṭainta taravaṇaimē laivarkkā yaṉṟu</l>
<l>miṭaintatu pārata vempō – ruṭaintatuvu</l>
<l>māyccipāṉ mattukkē yammaṉē vāḷeyiṟṟup</l>
<l>pēyccipā luṇṭa pirāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He settled on the serpent bed, being of the Five [Pāṇḍavas] that day</l>
<l>he was mingled  in the hot Bhārata war, and he was dejected</l>
<l>because of the churning stick in [the hand of] the cowherdess, o mother,</l>
<l>the lord who had drunk the milk of the demoness with sharp teeth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
